      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic blood pump geometry at flow rates of 2.5, 3.5, and 5.0 L/min and rotational speeds of 2500 and 3500 RPM, spanning the COU operating envelope. Geometric similarity between validation and COU configurations was confirmed by dimensional analysis."
